      "rationale": "The k-omega SST turbulence model was selected based on general rotating machinery practice. No turbulence model sensitivity study was performed for the hemolysis QoI. The power-law hemolysis damage model (Giersiepen constants) was applied without re-calibration to the specific blood analog or pump geometry. Model form uncertainty is uncharacterized for the primary QoI."
